title: Funkoars the greatest hits live - Soon13 DVDrip
description: Since the release of their sophomore album 'The Greatest Hits' in 2006, Adelaide's Funkoars have attained cult-like status with their incredible live performances and notorious on-stage antics. Returning to their home town for a one-off show in August 2007, Sesta, Hons, Trials & DJ Reflux pounded the stage with the energy that has made them a phenomenon. Superbly captured with incredible audio and vision, 'The Greatest Hits Live' DVD is as close as you'll get to the front row and still remain dry. It features the incredible HQ performance along with exclusive interviews and rare studio footage, offering an insight into one of Australia's most unique groups
